welcome_message_title: Welcome to San Felipe del Progreso
welcome_message_body: Welcome to San Felipe del Progreso, a charming city known for its vibrant culture and rich history. We invite you to explore our beautiful streets, taste our delicious cuisine, and enjoy all the wonders this city has to offer. Bienvenidos!
